{"tid":296653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無公屋撚裝修到間屋好靚?","createTime":"2017-06-24T18:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T22:27:48.000Z","uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89a640aa5268978f30f2f8ca1584f4b51f31c936","tid":296653,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"好似私樓既現代化裝修?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n眼見D公屋唔打理唔裝修真係好似垃圾堆田區咁，野又舊又多污積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455a4ba34811522dd4c88b6386e1834298440ada","tid":296653,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似私樓既現代化裝修?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n眼見D公屋唔打理唔裝修真係好似垃圾堆田區咁，野又舊又多污積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂豪裝公屋其實好柒，上網search啲例子，全部好老土<br />\n公屋裝修畀盡都係10萬，唔通整個背光假天花<br />\n<br />\n其實最簡單走牆線，油靚油，鋪靚個木地板，啲傢私唔好又大件又食位就已經好正<br />\n<br />\n根本唔關靚裝修事，只係有啲人真係唔介意間屋企要咁企理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2b14ee15ed4742cd3fec7a5bbfd7776407926b","tid":296653,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:06:44.000Z","msg":"所謂善用空間果堆真係唔好搞"},{"pid":"3a167c98172987a14e4093fbe41fd95c9f4ee35e","tid":296653,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T22:27:48.000Z","msg":"無空間點整都唔靚<br />\n間屋夠大就咁放張枱都可以好靚"}]}